[normal]What should the BBC be for and what should be the purpose of public service broadcasting?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]How well has the BBC performed in the current Charter period in achieving its mission and public purposes?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Are the public [bold]purposes in the current Charter the right ones? How might they change?[bold]&#xa0;
