[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]What scope, scale and remit should the BBC have?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Should the BBC’s output[bold] and services be provided to any greater or lesser degree for particular audiences?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]What balance should be struck in what the BBC produces in-house, commissions externally and leaves entirely to others to create?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
