[normal]How have the BBC’s commercial activities during the current Charter fitted with the BBC’s public[bold] [bold]purposes and have they achieved an adequate return for licence fee [bold]payers? What should be the aims, scope and scale of such activities beyond 2016?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
