[normal]How should the BBC be funded beyond 2016?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Is there a case for distributing funding for public service content more widely beyond the BBC?[bold]What comparisons[bold] can be made with the provision of public service content in other countries?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
