[normal]How should the BBC be [bold]governed, regulated and held accountable beyond 2016?[bold]In a constantly evolving communications environment, does a 10-year Royal Charter and Agreement with the Secretary of State, together, provide the most appropriate constitutional framework for the BBC?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
